# LLM Training Data Pipeline

## Overview

This project collects, cleans, standardizes, and categorizes training datasets for a general-purpose AI assistant.

## Datasets Used

- Dolly 15K
- Alpaca
- OpenAssistant
- WikiText-103
- CNN/DailyMail
- BoolQ

## Features

- Dataset acquisition
- Data cleaning
- Schema standardization
- Conversation reconstruction
- Dataset categorization
- Final corpus generation

## Technologies

- Python
- Pandas
- Hugging Face Datasets